fulltitle: Vincent Herring Masterclass: “Synthetic Pentatonics & Diminished Scales” + Q&A
description:
VINCENT HERRING Masterclass "Synthetic Pentatonics & Diminished Scales” LIVE Masterclass + Q&A! DETAILS: http://JazzHeaven.com/live
#vincentherring #jazzheaven #jazzmasterclass
Vincent covered:
"Synthetic Pentatonics & Diminished Scales”

* Using Pentatonics and Synthetic Pentatonics in Improvisation

* Breaking down the Diminished Scale to create Modern Vocabulary

* And a lot more! ;)

Masterclass + Q&A + 1-on-1 HOT SEATS where YOU can be live on screen via webcam & get 1-on-1 Feedback from Vincent!

Details: http://JazzHeaven.com/live

About VINCENT HERRING:

One of the finest alto sax players, Vincent has appeared on stage and or recordings with Freddie Hubbard, Dizzy Gillespie, Louis Hayes, Art Blakey & the Jazz Messengers, Horace Silver Quintet, Jack DeJohnette’s Special Edition, The Mingus Big Band (Won a Grammy in 2010), Kenny Barron, Nancy Wilson, Dr. Billy Taylor, Carla Bley & many others.

His extensive guest soloist appearances include performances with Wynton Marsalis at Lincoln Center and Jon Faddis and The Carnegie Hall Big Band.

As an educator, he is currently on staff at William Paterson University and at Manhattan School of Music.

Details: http://JazzHeaven.com/live
